after npm installs etc


npm i mongodb@3.5.7  to install mongo driver in the server folder

we now go to server.js 

router. post() refers to POST requests and
router. get() referes to GET request. The difference between the two is that a GET request,
is requesting data from a specified source and a POST request submits data to a specified resource to be processed



all the routers are going into sightings 